<div class="music-list" style="margin-top:20px;"><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/befriended.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/bfriendted.jpg" alt="Befriended / The Innocence Mission" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/befriended.php">Befriended<br />The Innocence Mission</a></h4><p>やわらかく、優しいアコースティックギターとささやきかけるようなヴォーカルが家でのひとときをふんわりと包んでくれます。食事やリビングでかけるのがおすすめです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003HOUKL0?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003HOUKL0" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Befriended-The Innocence Mission']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fbefriended%252Fid377376369%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Befriended-The Innocence Mission']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/post-53.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/nihonnouta01.jpg" alt="にほんのうた 第一集 / Various Artists" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/post-53.php">にほんのうた 第一集<br />Various Artists</a></h4><p>子供と一緒にこの音楽を聴いてみませんか？誰もが知っているあの音楽をセンスのよい音で聴けます。寝る前にプレイするのもおすすめです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000UVXIGW?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000UVXIGW" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'にほんのうた 第一集-Various Artists']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnihonno-uta-di1syu%252Fid266179240%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'にほんのうた 第一集-Various Artists']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/takk.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/takk.jpg" alt="Takk... / Sigur Ros" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/takk.php">Takk...<br />Sigur Ros</a></h4><p>静かな朝などにプレイするのもおすすめです。シガー・ロスならではの落ち着いた雰囲気と優しい音色が家族を優しく包み込んでくれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000AJJNPY?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000AJJNPY" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Takk...-Sigur Ros']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ftakk%252Fid141731594%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Takk...-Sigur Ros']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/people-project.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/pepole.jpg" alt="People Project / People Project" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/people-project.php">People Project<br />People Project</a></h4><p>昼間にこれを聴きながらお茶を飲むのよし、会話をしながらBGMとしても流せる、ブラジル音楽とアフロ音楽の中間のようなサウンドがとても気持ちよい作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000RNUJ60?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000RNUJ60" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'People Project-People Project']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fpeople-project%252Fid265832415%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'People Project-People Project']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/gling-glo.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/glingglo.jpg" alt="Gling-Glo / Bjork" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/gling-glo.php">Gling-Glo<br />Bjork</a></h4><p>夜の食事にかけてみるのはいかがでしょうか。優しい雰囲気があるので子供がいてもかけられます。ビョークのジャズアルバムです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00000AOQG?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00000AOQG" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Gling-Glo-Bjork']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fgling-glo%252Fid73197907%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Gling-Glo-Bjork']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/you-are-my-little-bird.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/youaremyit.jpg" alt="You Are My Little Bird / Elizabeth Mitchell" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/you-are-my-little-bird.php">You Are My Little Bird<br />Elizabeth Mitchell</a></h4><p>子供のために作られたという音楽。フォーキーで親しみやすいサウンドなので歌いながら遊ぶこともできるでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000GKZN9M?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000GKZN9M" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'You Are My Little Bird-Elizabeth Mitchell']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fyou-are-my-little-bird%252Fid219402664%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'You Are My Little Bird-Elizabeth Mitchell']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/the-future-will-come.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/futurewillcome.jpg" alt="The Future Will Come / The Juan MacLean" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/the-future-will-come.php">The Future Will Come<br />The Juan MacLean</a></h4><p>アコースティックではありませんが、明るい音楽なので家族の団らんでプレイするには最適の作品です。元気を出したいという方におすすめです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001SZ27HA?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001SZ27HA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Future Will Come-The Juan MacLean']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-future-will-come%252Fid317203569%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Future Will Come-The Juan MacLean']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/juanita.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/juanita.jpg" alt="Juanita / Roman Andren" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/juanita.php">Juanita<br />Roman Andren</a></h4><p>音の質感がとても心地よい音楽。グルーヴもとても心地よいので何度聴いても飽きさせません。家族での旅行に持参してはいかがでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000XFQA74?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000XFQA74" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Juanita-Roman Andren']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fjuanita%252Fid270823784%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Juanita-Roman Andren']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/the-reminder.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/reminder.jpg" alt="The Reminder / Feist" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/the-reminder.php">The Reminder<br />Feist</a></h4><p>カナダのアーティスト。昼の落ち着いたひとときに自宅で聴いてみるのもよいでしょう。少しゆったりとしたい時におすすめです。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000NPE7YC?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000NPE7YC" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Reminder-Feist']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-reminder%252Fid220155357%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Reminder-Feist']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

